class="card card-featured"><h1 class="card-title">
Simple Website Examples - 5 Sites That Simply Work</h1><div
class="card-body"><div
class="card-text card-text-prebyline">We combed through hundreds of sites to find website examples that are simple, yet still accomplish everything they need to.</div><div
class="card-byline"><div
class="card-byline-image">
<img
class="lazyload"
data-src="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-paul-peters-800x800-2024057.webp?crop=1:1,smart&width=80&dpr=2"
width="80"
height="80"
alt="Paul Peters"
/></div><div
class="card-byline-details">
<span>By <a
class="card-byline-author" href="https://www.notzarla.com/contributors/paul-peters">Paul Peters</a>,</span>
<span
class="card-byline-date">Jul 24, 2024</span><div
class="card-byline-bio">
Paul Peters is the Editor in Chief of Zarla. He&#039;s a former print journalist and small business owner. He has designed websites and logos for several small businesses he founded.</div></div></div></div><div
class="card-image-holder"><div
class="card-preview">
<picture>
<source
srcset="https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-simple-websites-3840x2400-20242407.png?crop=2:1,smart&width=372 1x, https://www.notzarla.com/images/zarla-simple-websites-3840x2400-20242407.png?crop=2:1,smart&width=372&dpr=2 2x"
